rth.  I activated my lights and sirens and pulled over the car.  The driver was IDed and found that there was problems with his documentation.  I tickted him and cleared the traffic stop.  I then received a call from dispatch of suspcious drug actvity in town.  I then arrived and found the suspected person in the middle of a park.  I walked slowly towards him and IDed myself as a police officer.  The defendeant then pulled a firearm on me and shot twice.  I pulled my service weapon, shot and killed him.  I then called an ambulance to come and clear the scene.9/10  Would kill drug dealers againRe-Edit to the trolls* To those trolls who say 1.8 hours.  I am in business and am on the road playing offline more than online.  Offline hours do not count towards my hours played total.  Thanks"
